  <Document>
    <name>Calamorro Mountain, Benalmadena</name>
    <description>Ascent of Monte Calamorro from Tivoli World, Benalmadena, 25 May 2011. Recorded on Garmin. 9.4 km, ~660 m climb. Recovered from Garmin Connect (activity 472257121) after the original KML was lost in the WordPress-to-Jekyll migration.</description>
